=Title: {{ $json.body.title }}
JD: {{ $json.body.full_job_description }}

Extract 10 concise and impactful key phrases that best represent the JD’s hiring intent, focusing on role responsibilities, domain-specific skills, tools/technologies, and measurable business outcomes.  
Exclude generic or vague terms (e.g., "team", "responsible", "communication", "dynamic environment") and ensure the 10 selected keywords can directly guide resume customization and experience tailoring.  

Output strictly as two separate fields in JSON format:

{
  "Title": "{{ $json.title }}",
  "Keywords": ["keyword1", "keyword2", "keyword3", ... , "keyword10"]
}

Do not include any explanations, introductions, or extra text.
